      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "85efc0594ebbc080",
      "text": "In [[AIC]] influence refers to the domain of political awareness, negotiation, coalition building in order to move toward action--creating something, removing something, or holding things as near the same as possible. This is where diversity is made visible and arrangements made for action."
    },
